00:38:48,160 --> 00:38:50,040
 Ali čini to na Franji način,

933
00:38:50,040 --> 00:38:51,140
 unutar crkve.

934
00:38:51,140 --> 00:38:53,380
 Jer tako izgrađujemo

935
00:38:53,380 --> 00:38:55,660
 mistično tijelo Kristovo crkvu

936
00:38:55,660 --> 00:38:56,660
 koji smo pozvani

937
00:38:56,660 --> 00:38:58,020
 po svom pozivu,

938
00:38:58,020 --> 00:38:59,500
 po sakramentu krštenja,

939
00:38:59,500 --> 00:39:01,620
 izgrađivati dok le god živimo.

940
00:39:02,080 --> 00:39:02,560
 Hvala djepo.

